{"sn7.6:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 7.6 ","sn7.6:0.2":"1. Arahantavagga ","sn7.6:0.3":"Jatasutta ","sn7.6:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn7.6:1.2":"Atha kho jatabharadvajo brahmano yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavata saddhim sammodi. ","sn7.6:1.3":"Sammodaniyam katham saraniyam vitisaretva ekamantam nisidi. ","sn7.6:1.4":"Ekamantam nisinno kho jatabharadvajo brahmano bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn7.6:2.1":"“Antojata bahijata, ","sn7.6:2.2":"Jataya jatita paja; ","sn7.6:2.3":"Tam tam gotama pucchami, ","sn7.6:2.4":"Ko imam vijataye jatan”ti. ","sn7.6:3.1":"“Sile patitthaya naro sapanno, ","sn7.6:3.2":"Cittam pannanca bhavayam; ","sn7.6:3.3":"Atapi nipako bhikkhu, ","sn7.6:3.4":"So imam vijataye jatam. ","sn7.6:4.1":"Yesam rago ca doso ca, ","sn7.6:4.2":"avijja ca virajita; ","sn7.6:4.3":"Khinasava arahanto, ","sn7.6:4.4":"tesam vijatita jata. ","sn7.6:5.1":"Yattha namanca rupanca, ","sn7.6:5.2":"asesam uparujjhati; ","sn7.6:5.3":"Patigham rupasanna ca, ","sn7.6:5.4":"etthesa chijjate jata”ti. ","sn7.6:6.1":"Evam vutte, jatabharadvajo bhagavantam etadavoca: ","sn7.6:6.2":"“abhikkantam, bho gotama …pe… ","sn7.6:6.3":"annataro ca panayasma bharadvajo arahatam ahosi”ti. "}